# Generated Output - Do Not Edit

This directory contains generated static site output. **Do not edit files here manually.**

All files are regenerated by the build process and manual changes will be lost.

## How to Make Changes

| What to Change | Playbook |
|----------------|----------|
| Page content | `systemprompt core playbooks show build_web-content` |
| Templates | `systemprompt core playbooks show build_web-templates` |
| CSS/Assets | `systemprompt core playbooks show build_web-assets` |
| Site structure | `systemprompt core playbooks show build_web-pages` |

## Regenerate Output

```bash
systemprompt web build
```

## Source Locations

- **Content**: `services/content/`
- **Templates**: `services/web/templates/`
- **Config**: `services/web/config.yaml`
